                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Brown</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.—Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-07-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 18, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Brown reports that President Estrada deeply appreciates effective
                    cooperation of President Diaz and has cordially invited Mexican minister to
                    attend peace negotiations.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
